2. Keep express in watch mode
   tool: https://github.com/remy/nodemon
   command: nodemon conFUNrence

3. Run forever
   tool: https://github.com/Unitech/pm2
   start: pm2 start npm -- start 
   stop: pm2 stop all  
   log: pm2 logs

